=== RADICAL_SPRING ===
# id: 76
# title: The Radical Spring
# chinese_title: 本源之泉
# category: Shrine
# mode: dungeon

Water flows upward from the floor in defiance of gravity, forming characters in mid-air before dissolving back into mist. Each character is a radical in its purest form. The spring seems ancient, far older than the station built around it. Drinking from it is said to grant understanding.

* [Drink from the spring]
  ~ gain_radical("水")
  "泉" (quán) — spring, fountain. Contains the radical "水" (shuǐ).
* [Collect the water in a container]
  ~ gain_item("biogel_patch")
  "集" (jí) — to collect, to gather
* [Meditate beside the spring]
  ~ heal(15)
  "清" (qīng) — clear, pure, clean
